SECURITY WARNING - PLEASE READ
================================================================================

This software handles sensitive security data including passwords, entropy,
and cryptographic operations. By using this software, you acknowledge and
accept the following:

YOU USE THIS SOFTWARE ENTIRELY AT YOUR OWN RISK.

This software:
- Has NOT been independently audited or formally verified
- Has NOT undergone widespread security review
- May contain bugs, vulnerabilities, or design flaws
- Is developed by an individual, not a security team
- Should NOT be your only line of defense for critical security

The author makes NO guarantees about:
- The cryptographic soundness of any implementation
- The security of generated passwords, usernames, or entropy
- The integrity of data stored or managed by this software
- Compatibility with future versions of 1Password or other dependencies

If you are using this software for anything important:
- Maintain independent backups
- Verify critical operations manually
- Consider professional security review before production use
- Understand the code before trusting it with sensitive data

YOU HAVE BEEN WARNED.

By using this software, you accept full responsibility for any consequences,
including but not limited to data loss, security breaches, or any other
damages that may result from its use.

